msgid ""
"For example, settings populated through environment variables set to ``'one,"
"two'`` will return a list ['one', 'two'] when using this method."
msgstr ""
"例如，通过环境变量填充的设置设置设置为 ``'one,two'`` 时，会返回一个列表"
"['one','2']。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:270
msgid "Signals API"
msgstr "信号 API"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:279
msgid "Connect a receiver function to a signal."
msgstr "将接收器函数与信号连接起来。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:281
msgid ""
"The signal can be any object, although Scrapy comes with some predefined "
"signals that are documented in the :ref:`topics-signals` section."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:285
msgid "the function to be connected"
msgstr "要连接的函数"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:288
msgid "the signal to connect to"
msgstr "要连接到的信号"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:293
msgid "Send a signal, catch exceptions and log them."
msgstr "发送一个信号，捕获异常并记录它们。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:295 ../../../topics/api.rst:306
msgid ""
"The keyword arguments are passed to the signal handlers (connected through "
"the :meth:`connect` method)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:300
msgid ""
"Like :meth:`send_catch_log` but supports returning `deferreds`_ from signal "
"handlers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:303
msgid ""
"Returns a `deferred`_ that gets fired once all signal handlers deferreds "
"were fired. Send a signal, catch exceptions and log them."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:311
msgid ""
"Disconnect a receiver function from a signal. This has the opposite effect "
"of the :meth:`connect` method, and the arguments are the same."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:316
msgid "Disconnect all receivers from the given signal."
msgstr "断开所有接收器与给定信号的连接。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:318
msgid "the signal to disconnect from"
msgstr "要断开连接的信号"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:324
msgid "Stats Collector API"
msgstr "统计数据收集器 API"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:326
msgid ""
"There are several Stats Collectors available under the :mod:`scrapy."
"statscol` module and they all implement the Stats Collector API defined by "
"the :class:`~scrapy.statscol.StatsCollector` class (which they all inherit "
"from)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:338
msgid ""
"Return the value for the given stats key or default if it doesn't exist."
msgstr "返回给定状态键值或默认值，如果它不存在。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:342
msgid "Get all stats from the currently running spider as a dict."
msgstr "从当前运行的蜘蛛获取所有的统计信息作为一种词典。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:346
msgid "Set the given value for the given stats key."
msgstr "设置给定统计键的给定值。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:350
msgid "Override the current stats with the dict passed in ``stats`` argument."
msgstr "使用 ``stats`` 参数覆盖当前的统计信息。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:354
msgid ""
"Increment the value of the given stats key, by the given count, assuming the "
"start value given (when it's not set)."
msgstr ""
"通过给定的计数增加给定统计数据的值，假定给定的起始值 (当它没有设置时)。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:359
msgid ""
"Set the given value for the given key only if current value for the same key "
"is lower than value. If there is no current value for the given key, the "
"value is always set."
msgstr ""
"仅在同一键的当前值小于值时设置给定的键值。 如果给定的键值没有当前值，则该值总"
"是被设置的。"

#: ../../../topics/api.rst:365
msgid ""
"Set the given value for the given key only if current value for the same key "
"is greater than value. If there is no current value for the given key, the "
"value is always set."
msgstr ""
"只有当同一键的当前值大于值时，才设置给定的键值。 如果给定的键值没有当前值，则"
"该值总是被设置的。"

